{'title': 'ABN AMRO Clearing extends its relationship with Fidessa to include screen distribution', 'id': 'AMvbEo0ign61YeZD6bvoM', 'introduction': "October 16, 2017 – Fidessa group plc (LSE: FDSA) today announced that it has extended its existing relationship with ABN AMRO Clearing Bank N.V. to allow the global clearer to distribute Fidessa’s derivatives EMS. In June 2016 ABN Amro Clearing harmonised its global multi-asset market access by replacing numerous ISV and in-house systems with Fidessa's XTP technology. ABN Amro Clearing can now present its clients with a globally consistent and highly performant market access layer to more than 110 futures, options, equities and FX markets delivered out of 11 key locations around the world.\n", 'createdAt': 0, 'publicationDate': 1508168700000, 'updatedAt': 1607548203515, 'topStory': False, 'slugs': [{'locale': 'en', 'value': 'abn-amro-clearing-extends-its-relationship-with-fidessa-to-include-screen'}], 'image': {'title': 'ABN AMRO Clearing extends its relationship with Fidessa to include screen distribution', 'url': '//images.ctfassets.net/1u811bvgvthc/2ouSiaczwtadfxWqJW2APD/4197e741b80254ca8d66566e944d9e7a/Fidessa_ABN.jpg', 'size': 10478.0, 'type': 'image/jpeg', 'fileExtension': 'jpg', 'createdDate': 0}, 'mainText': None, 'contact': None, 'businessLines': None, 'categories': ['Press release'], 'location': None, 'video': None, 'relatedArticles': None, 'reactions': None, 'tags': [{'id': '4F4qNf3duk0Tk7hobOrAdX', 'value': 'Clearing'}], 'tagline': None, 'showOverviewImage': True}
{'title': 'ABN AMRO Clearing Contracts with Trading Technologies to Distribute the TT® Platform', 'id': '2OnN7wTFDc3yjOO6jOc2fW', 'introduction': 'LONDON and AMSTERDAM, June 6, 2017 – ABN AMRO Clearing Bank N.V. and Trading Technologies International, Inc. (TT), a global provider of high-performance professional trading software, today announced ABN AMRO Clearing has contracted to make available the TT trading platform to ABN AMRO Clearing’s customers globally. This agreement furthers the long-standing partnership between Trading Technologies and ABN AMRO Clearing, which is also a distributor of TT’s legacy X_TRADER® platform. \n', 'createdAt': 0, 'publicationDate': 1496751780000, 'updatedAt': 1607548203512, 'topStory': False, 'slugs': [{'locale': 'en', 'value': 'abn-amro-clearing-contracts-with-trading-technologies-to-distribute-the-tt-r'}], 'image': {'title': '840x473-Gustav en Cirl', 'url': '//images.ctfassets.net/1u811bvgvthc/7nmgmD6MorBVQap4gtV3tB/9f0a97113bc4a8f63bffdaabcc0a977b/840x473-Gustav-en-circl_website-abn-amro-tai.jpg', 'size': 114931.0, 'type': 'image/jpeg', 'fileExtension': 'jpg', 'createdDate': 0}, 'mainText': None, 'contact': None, 'businessLines': None, 'categories': ['Press release'], 'location': None, 'video': None, 'relatedArticles': None, 'reactions': None, 'tags': [{'id': '4F4qNf3duk0Tk7hobOrAdX', 'value': 'Clearing'}], 'tagline': None, 'showOverviewImage': True}
{'title': 'OCC appoints 2 new members to the Board of Directors', 'id': '2INvW0i5WeBZXNHPhwPjG1', 'introduction': 'CHICAGO, March 30, 2017 OCC, the world’s largest equity derivatives clearing organization, today announced that Andrej Bolkovic, CEO of ABN AMRO Clearing Chicago LLC, and Jamil Nazarali, Head of Execution Services at Citadel Securities, have joined the board of directors as Member Directors.\n', 'createdAt': 0, 'publicationDate': 1490868000000, 'updatedAt': 1607548427819, 'topStory': False, 'slugs': [{'locale': 'en', 'value': 'occ-appoints-2-new-members-to-the-board-of-directors'}], 'image': {'title': '840x473-Gustav en Cirl', 'url': '//images.ctfassets.net/1u811bvgvthc/7nmgmD6MorBVQap4gtV3tB/9f0a97113bc4a8f63bffdaabcc0a977b/840x473-Gustav-en-circl_website-abn-amro-tai.jpg', 'size': 114931.0, 'type': 'image/jpeg', 'fileExtension': 'jpg', 'createdDate': 0}, 'mainText': None, 'contact': None, 'businessLines': None, 'categories': ['Press release'], 'location': None, 'video': None, 'relatedArticles': None, 'reactions': None, 'tags': [{'id': '4F4qNf3duk0Tk7hobOrAdX', 'value': 'Clearing'}], 'tagline': None, 'showOverviewImage': True}
