{'title': 'DGCX Group welcome ABN AMRO Clearing Bank N.V. as Special Clearing member', 'id': '5YOrsra62PTue3Zwd0zGZU', 'introduction': 'Dubai, October 11, 2016: Dubai Gold and Commodities Exchange (DGCX) welcomed ABN AMRO Clearing Bank N.V. as a Special Clearing Member on Dubai Commodities Clearing Corporation (DCCC). DCCC is a wholly owned subsidiary of DGCX and acts as central counterparty for all trades executed on the Exchange. ', 'createdAt': 0, 'publicationDate': 1476186540000, 'updatedAt': 1607549140343, 'topStory': False, 'slugs': [{'locale': 'en', 'value': 'dgcx-group-welcome-abn-amro-clearing-bank-n-v-as-special-clearing-member'}], 'image': {'title': 'DGCX logo 3', 'url': '//images.ctfassets.net/1u811bvgvthc/2dCQRRGwAuXgkvD1YWyYsN/1aad95bd054211fcffda2f3bf53627b7/DGCX_logo_3.jpg', 'size': 216704.0, 'type': 'image/jpeg', 'fileExtension': 'jpg', 'createdDate': 0}, 'mainText': None, 'contact': None, 'businessLines': None, 'categories': ['Press release'], 'location': None, 'video': None, 'relatedArticles': None, 'reactions': None, 'tags': [{'id': '4F4qNf3duk0Tk7hobOrAdX', 'value': 'Clearing'}], 'tagline': None, 'showOverviewImage': True}
{'title': 'Devet Capital Investments wins AIF Factor at the Amsterdam Investor Forum 2016', 'id': '5lqYzKXOxpiBvBdO2DVEdi', 'introduction': 'During ABN AMRO Clearing’s 5th Amsterdam Investor Forum on 17 February 2016, Devet Capital Investments was voted the AIF Factor 2016 winner. The fund successfully pitched their investment strategy and convinced a group of over 250 delegates, comprising of investment managers, institutional investors, Hedge funds allocators, high net worth individuals and a jury panel consisting of four industry experts. It was a very close call and a special mention goes to Mint Tower who came narrowly in second place by 0.6%.\n', 'createdAt': 0, 'publicationDate': 1455699900000, 'updatedAt': 1607549140450, 'topStory': False, 'slugs': [{'locale': 'en', 'value': 'devet-capital-investments-wins-aif-factor-at-the-amsterdam-investor-forum'}], 'image': {'title': 'Devet Capital Investments wins AIF Factor 2016 at the Amsterdam Investor Forum', 'url': '//images.ctfassets.net/1u811bvgvthc/4Y6GCZY3q9642AIqHO2ybg/2af7fe8e992fb498ba92b69e0452268a/970x404_AIF_winner.jpg', 'size': 196119.0, 'type': 'image/jpeg', 'fileExtension': 'jpg', 'createdDate': 0}, 'mainText': None, 'contact': None, 'businessLines': None, 'categories': ['Press release'], 'location': None, 'video': None, 'relatedArticles': None, 'reactions': None, 'tags': [{'id': '4F4qNf3duk0Tk7hobOrAdX', 'value': 'Clearing'}], 'tagline': None, 'showOverviewImage': True}
{'title': 'ABN AMRO Clearing announces 5 finalists in the AIF Factor 2016 competition', 'id': '5SHwlw4FHXS5NpFCu3A1Ew', 'introduction': 'Five alternative investment funds have been selected, by a jury panel consisting of industry experts, to compete in The AIF Factor on February 17th, 2016 during the Amsterdam Investor Forum (AIF), organised by ABN AMRO Clearing. In a 3 minutes pitch the funds will present their strategy and delegates as well as the jury will cast their votes to elect the “AIF Factor Winner for 2016”.\n', 'createdAt': 0, 'publicationDate': 1453396920000, 'updatedAt': 1607548201604, 'topStory': False, 'slugs': [{'locale': 'en', 'value': 'abn-amro-clearing-announces-5-finalists-in-the-aif-factor-2016-competition'}], 'image': {'title': 'ABN AMRO Clearing announces 5 finalists in the AIF Factor 2016 competition', 'url': '//images.ctfassets.net/1u811bvgvthc/6TzeP9enMoEIBDj2PR2hTR/c5aa0d2e2dfe60f57b599983e6af9932/970x404_Capture.jpg', 'size': 106152.0, 'type': 'image/jpeg', 'fileExtension': 'jpg', 'createdDate': 0}, 'mainText': None, 'contact': None, 'businessLines': None, 'categories': ['Press release'], 'location': None, 'video': None, 'relatedArticles': None, 'reactions': None, 'tags': [{'id': '4F4qNf3duk0Tk7hobOrAdX', 'value': 'Clearing'}], 'tagline': None, 'showOverviewImage': True}
