{'title': 'ABN AMRO Clearing voted ‘Proprietary Traders Clearing Firm of the Year’ in industry awards', 'id': '2drHfnFYE0fYUkVWu2vLAe', 'introduction': 'The awards were voted on by over 100 global proprietary trading firms and opinions were canvassed across a range of categories. ABN AMRO Clearing was praised for its excellent customer service, account management and product offering. The Risk Management teams also stood out thanks to their risk system (developed in-house) and partnership approach to business.\n', 'createdAt': 0, 'publicationDate': 1418169600000, 'updatedAt': 1607548232715, 'topStory': False, 'slugs': [{'locale': 'en', 'value': 'abn-amro-clearing-voted-proprietary-traders-clearing-firm-of-the-year'}], 'image': {'title': '840x473-Gustav en Cirl', 'url': '//images.ctfassets.net/1u811bvgvthc/7nmgmD6MorBVQap4gtV3tB/9f0a97113bc4a8f63bffdaabcc0a977b/840x473-Gustav-en-circl_website-abn-amro-tai.jpg', 'size': 114931.0, 'type': 'image/jpeg', 'fileExtension': 'jpg', 'createdDate': 0}, 'mainText': None, 'contact': None, 'businessLines': None, 'categories': ['Press release'], 'location': None, 'video': None, 'relatedArticles': None, 'reactions': None, 'tags': [{'id': '4F4qNf3duk0Tk7hobOrAdX', 'value': 'Clearing'}], 'tagline': None, 'showOverviewImage': True}
{'title': 'ABN AMRO offers investment funds an international podium', 'id': 'KjA4PIebqTZ4kjTbvvTgz', 'introduction': 'The Amsterdam Investor Forum (AIF) offers alternative funds a podium to present themselves to a group of over 200 professional investors. As of today interested funds can apply and enter into the competition. On 11 February, the 6 shortlisted funds will have the floor for a 3 minute pitch during the conference, which takes place at ABN AMRO headquarters in Amsterdam.', 'createdAt': 0, 'publicationDate': 1416355200000, 'updatedAt': 1607548262331, 'topStory': False, 'slugs': [{'locale': 'en', 'value': 'abn-amro-offers-investment-funds-an-international-podium'}], 'image': {'title': '840x473-Gustav en Cirl', 'url': '//images.ctfassets.net/1u811bvgvthc/7nmgmD6MorBVQap4gtV3tB/9f0a97113bc4a8f63bffdaabcc0a977b/840x473-Gustav-en-circl_website-abn-amro-tai.jpg', 'size': 114931.0, 'type': 'image/jpeg', 'fileExtension': 'jpg', 'createdDate': 0}, 'mainText': None, 'contact': None, 'businessLines': None, 'categories': ['Press release'], 'location': None, 'video': None, 'relatedArticles': None, 'reactions': None, 'tags': [{'id': '4F4qNf3duk0Tk7hobOrAdX', 'value': 'Clearing'}], 'tagline': None, 'showOverviewImage': True}
{'title': 'Northern Trust and AAC help Dutch Institutional Investors Respond to Regulatory Challenges', 'id': '1T0jkrJGZ2dV3ChO0QZ4tQ', 'introduction': 'Under the terms of the collaboration ABN AMRO Clearing will provide derivatives clearing services which, combined with Northern Trust’s custody and collateral management services, will help clients respond to the new regulatory requirements and reduce the burden of the transition to a cleared derivative environment.', 'createdAt': 0, 'publicationDate': 1412208000000, 'updatedAt': 1607548428710, 'topStory': False, 'slugs': [{'locale': 'en', 'value': 'northern-trust-and-aac-help-dutch-institutional-investors-respond-to'}], 'image': {'title': '840x473-Gustav en Cirl', 'url': '//images.ctfassets.net/1u811bvgvthc/7nmgmD6MorBVQap4gtV3tB/9f0a97113bc4a8f63bffdaabcc0a977b/840x473-Gustav-en-circl_website-abn-amro-tai.jpg', 'size': 114931.0, 'type': 'image/jpeg', 'fileExtension': 'jpg', 'createdDate': 0}, 'mainText': None, 'contact': None, 'businessLines': None, 'categories': ['Press release'], 'location': None, 'video': None, 'relatedArticles': None, 'reactions': None, 'tags': [{'id': '4F4qNf3duk0Tk7hobOrAdX', 'value': 'Clearing'}], 'tagline': None, 'showOverviewImage': True}
{'title': 'HCH is pleased to introduce Intercontinental Exchange as the new majority shareholder in HCH', 'id': '7DUIyWxSQIDPtbComEzeXO', 'introduction': 'HCH is pleased to introduce Intercontinental Exchange (ICE) as the new majority shareholder in HCH. ICE has entered into an agreement with ABN AMRO Clearing Bank to acquire a majority share in HCH. ABN AMRO Clearing Bank will remain a minority shareholder. Completion of the transaction is subject to regulatory approval and other closing conditions. The transaction is expected to close in the fourth quarter of 2014.', 'createdAt': 0, 'publicationDate': 1410393600000, 'updatedAt': 1607548622992, 'topStory': False, 'slugs': [{'locale': 'en', 'value': 'hch-is-pleased-to-introduce-intercontinental-exchange-as-the-new-majority'}], 'image': {'title': 'HCH logo small', 'url': '//images.ctfassets.net/1u811bvgvthc/2ruQ6kcaMPkymDJQYNCMv7/bb12b8dba9883d7b495b18418c17dcb9/HCH_logo_small.png', 'size': 13190.0, 'type': 'image/png', 'fileExtension': 'png', 'createdDate': 0}, 'mainText': None, 'contact': None, 'businessLines': None, 'categories': ['Press release'], 'location': None, 'video': None, 'relatedArticles': None, 'reactions': None, 'tags': [{'id': '4F4qNf3duk0Tk7hobOrAdX', 'value': 'Clearing'}], 'tagline': None, 'showOverviewImage': True}
{'title': 'Eyck Capital Management winner at Amsterdam Investor Forum 2014', 'id': '5VboEpnIHOVJ7I4LjyEe3Q', 'introduction': "Eyck Capital Management's Eyck European Tactical Distressed Opportunities Fund won ‘The AIF Factor’ competition at yesterday's 3rd Amsterdam Investor Forum organised by ABN AMRO Clearing. The fund was voted the clear winner out of six shortlisted alternative investment funds which made three minute 'elevator' pitches to 200 delegates, comprising institutional investors, funds of funds, high net worth individuals and a panel of seed investors.", 'createdAt': 0, 'publicationDate': 1392249600000, 'updatedAt': 1607548721861, 'topStory': False, 'slugs': [{'locale': 'en', 'value': 'eyck-capital-management-winner-at-amsterdam-investor-forum-2014'}], 'image': {'title': '840x473-Gustav en Cirl', 'url': '//images.ctfassets.net/1u811bvgvthc/7nmgmD6MorBVQap4gtV3tB/9f0a97113bc4a8f63bffdaabcc0a977b/840x473-Gustav-en-circl_website-abn-amro-tai.jpg', 'size': 114931.0, 'type': 'image/jpeg', 'fileExtension': 'jpg', 'createdDate': 0}, 'mainText': None, 'contact': None, 'businessLines': None, 'categories': ['Press release'], 'location': None, 'video': None, 'relatedArticles': None, 'reactions': None, 'tags': [{'id': '4F4qNf3duk0Tk7hobOrAdX', 'value': 'Clearing'}], 'tagline': None, 'showOverviewImage': True}
